7518.name: Donath's' Note - Vol.1
7518.description: A note that has cooking tips written by Donath.

7519.name: Shaved Ice
7519.description: Lilly's most favorite dessert that is made of a mixture of shaved ice and sweet flavorings.

7520.name: Ice Cream
7520.description: Sweet, soft and cold scoop of ice cream.

7521.name: Ice Crystal Gemstone
7521.description: When sunlight reflects on it, it shines brightly with a rainbow of colors.

7522.name: Offering
7522.description: Food that is dedicated to Saint Agnes. It is tightly sealed to preserve its freshness.

7526.name: Ancient Language Dictionary
7526.description: A dictionary that is used to decipher an ancient language.

7527.name: Ancient Language Dictionary
7527.description: A dictionary that is used to decipher an ancient language.

7528.name: Spinneret
7528.description: A spider's anatomical structure from which spider web is produced.

7529.name: Investigative Report
7529.description: A document received from Information Broker Mist. It contains the results of an investigation requested by Magister Justin.

7530.name: Investigative Report
7530.description: A document received from Information Broker Mist. It contains the results of an investigation requested by Magister Alminas.

7531.name: Investigative Report
7531.description: A document received from Information Broker Mist. It contains the results of an investigation requested by Magister Kamilen.

7532.name: Investigative Report
7532.description: A document received from Information Broker Bavarin. It contains the results of an investigation requested by Guard Baird.

7533.name: Investigative Report
7533.description: A document received from Information Broker Mist. It contains the results of an investigation requested by High Priest Gregory.

7534.name: Ice Cold Flower
7534.description: An ice crystal that is wrapped in fish scales and emits cold, icy air. Since it is beautifully created with a highly skilled hand, it looks like a flower.

7535.name: Pure Ice
7535.description: A chunk of purest ice that is made by freezing purified water. It is known to contain the power of the gods from the beginning of the world.

7536.name: Bitter Cold Beer
7536.description: The beer requested by Blacksmith Feynn. Just touching it makes your hands feel like they are freezing.

7537.name: Multiple Course Meal
7537.description: An elaborate meal requested by the Arena Manager. It is said to be eaten by duelists in ancient times to strengthen their stamina the day before their match.

7538.name: Dead Souls Fish Soup
7538.description: A soup that is supposed to contain all the nutrition of the fish it is made from. According to legend, depending on the fish you use to make it, it can have the effect of increasing or decreasing one's lifespan.

7539.name: Bitter Cold Vodka
7539.description: A legendary liquor that is made by dipping hot flames into cold, freezing ice. Although it feels cold to the lips it becomes hot in one's body.

7540.name: Silver Crystal
7540.description: The type of crystal that is needed to store wedding march music.

7541.name: Red Crystal
7541.description: The type of crystal that is needed to store birthday party music.

7542.name: Vampire's Heart
7542.description: The heart that is ripped out of the body of a vampire. It is still beating and pumping out blood.

7543.name: Zombie's Brain
7543.description: A piece of brain collected from an undead monster in the Forest of the Dead. It may contain the memory of the moment of its death.

7544.name: Rib Bone of a Black Magus
7544.description: The remaining bone that is left in the place where a necromancer died and disappeared. Perhaps it was used to transfix the shape of the necromancer.

7545.name: Zombie's Liver
7545.description: A liver that is rotting and emitting a strong stench. It is known to be a source of magical power of undead.

7546.name: Top Quality Meat
7546.description: A piece of top quality meat that is obtained by slaughtering a wild beast of proper age. Only one piece of this high quality meat can be obtained from one beast.

7547.name: Young Wild Beast Meat
7547.description: A piece of meat obtained by slaughtering a wild beast that is too young. Although it may have a pleasant aroma, it doesn't give good flavor when eating it.

7548.name: Map Piece
7548.description: A piece of a map that was once possessed by Monster Eyes.

7549.name: Yellow Map
7549.description: A map that contains a plot of the beasts. Take it to Mercenary Captain Sophya.

7550.name: Map Piece
7550.description: A piece of map obtained from the ghostly apparitions that haunt the Execution Grounds.

7551.name: Ivory Colored Map
7551.description: A map that contains strange information. By the way, sometime ago, Trader Galladucci complained that one of the maps he was supposed to receive didn't arrive...?

7552.name: Broken Gemstone Fragment
7552.description: A fragment of gemstone that can be obtained by hunting Maille Lizardmen.

7553.name: Gold Colored Gemstone
7553.description: A gold colored orb. High Priest Drikus is supposed to be looking for it.

7554.name: Scroll of Escape: Talking Island Village
7554.description: A magical scroll that relocates you to Talking Island. Scroll of Escape to Talking Island

7555.name: Scroll of Escape: Elven Village
7555.description: A magical scroll that relocates you to Elven Village. Scroll of Escape to Talking Island

7556.name: Scroll of Escape: Dark Elven Village
7556.description: A magical scroll that relocates you to Dark Elven Village. Scroll of Escape to Talking Island

7557.name: Scroll of Escape: Orc Village
7557.description: A magical scroll that relocates you to Orc Village. Scroll of Escape to Talking Island

7558.name: Scroll of Escape: Dwarven Village
7558.description: A magical scroll that relocates you to Dwarven Village. Scroll of Escape to Talking Island

7559.name: Scroll of Escape: Town of Giran
7559.description: A magical scroll that relocates you to Town of Giran. Scroll of Escape to Talking Island

7561.name: Fishing Manual
7561.description: An instructional book of fishing techniques. You can double-click it to read it.

7562.name: Dimensional Diamond
7562.description: A crystal that is filled with magical power. It is needed when casting Teleportation magic. If you collect this item and take them to a gatekeeper, you can trade them for various types of Scroll of Escape.

7563.name: Galladucci's Order (Document)
7563.description: A document with Galladucci's trader order. Take it to Trader Gentler at his magic shop.

7564.name: Galladucci's Order (Document)
7564.description: A document with Galladucci's trader order. Take it to Jeweler Sandra at her shop.

7565.name: Galladucci's Order (Document)
7565.description: A document with Galladucci's order. Take it to Priest Dustin at his shop.

7566.name: Purified Magic Necklace
7566.description: It's the item given by Priest Dustin. It seems to be the item Trader Galladucci has been looking for.

7567.name: Gemstone Powder
7567.description: The item given by Jeweler Sandra. This seems to be the item Trader Galladucci has been looking for.

7568.name: Magic Sword Hilt
7568.description: An item given by Trader Gentler. This seems to be the item Trader Galladucci has been looking for.

7569.name: Four-leaf Golden Clover Coin
7569.description: A gold coin that is engraved with a four-leaf clover design.

7570.name: Mark of Traveler
7570.description: A certificate to prove to Trader Galladucci the traveler's identity.

7571.name: Baulro's Letter
7571.description: The letter sent by Magister Baulro to Archon Sir Windawood.

7572.name: Ariel's Recommendation
7572.description: A letter of recommendation Trader Ariel wrote for you to be sent to Hierarch Asterios.

7573.name: Roselyn's Note
7573.description: A note Roselyn wrote while being angry and wrathful. You should deliver it to Magister Harne.

7574.name: Very Expensive Necklace
7574.description: A gift from Head Blacksmith Reed for Priest of the Earth Gerald. It looks very expensive.

7575.name: Draconic Bow
7575.description: Bestows one of the following functions: Cheap Shot, Focus, or Critical Slow.

7576.name: Draconic Bow - Cheap Shot
7576.description: <Soul Crystal Enhancement>. Has a 26% chance of decreasing MP consumption to 1 on a general attack. Increases damage inflicted during PvP. Special Ability: PvP Damage

7577.name: Draconic Bow - Focus
7577.description: <Soul Crystal Enhancement>. Increases Critical by 88. Increases damage inflicted during PvP. Special Ability: Focus

7578.name: Draconic Bow - Critical Slow
7578.description: <Soul Crystal Enhancement>. Has a chance of casting Slow on a critical attack. Increases damage inflicted during PvP. Special Ability: PvP Damage

7579.name: Draconic Bow Shaft
7579.description: Main ingredient essentially required for a Dwarf to make a Draconic Bow. Can also be sold at ordinary shops.

7580.name: Recipe: Draconic Bow (60%)
7580.description: For Dwarves only. The recipe for a Draconic Bow. Requires Create Item - Skill Level 9. The success rate is 60%.

7581.name: Recipe: Draconic Bow (100%)
7581.description: For Dwarves only. The recipe for a Draconic Bow. Requires Create Item - Skill Level 9. The success rate is 100%.

7582.name: Baby Spice
7582.description: When the food gauge of a baby buffalo, a baby cougar or a baby kookaburra drops to 55% or below, this feed will be consumed automatically. H5 Price Wolves' Food

7586.name: Sweet Fluid
7586.description: A type of fluid with a sweet fragrance. It is used as an ingredient to make a fishing shot.

7587.name: Legend of Seventeen
7587.description: A record of the seventeen heroes who fought against Antharas, the Land Dragon.

7588.name: Faded Poetry Book
7588.description: A poetry book written by an unknown Elven bard several hundred years ago.

7589.name: Echo Crystal - Forgotten Song
7589.description: An echo crystal that contains the song of Forgotten Heroes.

7590.name: Strand of Golden Hair
7590.description: A strand of hair that seems to have fallen from a blonde-haired lady.

7591.name: Ring of Goddess: Waterbinder
7591.description: Ring with a subtle blue gem. When picked up, it makes a sound like a flowing brook.

7592.name: Necklace of Goddess: EverGreen
7592.description: A necklace with a clear and bright bluish green crystal as a medallion. The moment when you hold it in your hand, you smell the scent of grass, wet with spring rain.

7593.name: Staff of Goddess: Rain Song
7593.description: A wooden staff that is embedded with a light blue orb at the top of it. It gives you a feeling of an ocean breeze filled with moisture blowing gently in your face.

7595.name: Orb of Binding
7595.description: A silver colored orb that emanates a strong feeling of magical power.

7596.name: Sorcery Ingredient
7596.description: A sorcery ingredient that is used by Witch Kalis.

7597.name: Malruk Succubus Claw
7597.description: Thin and sharp claw obtained from Malruk Succubus

7598.name: Crimson Moss
7598.description: Crimson Moss obtained from Swamp of Screams

7599.name: Rahorakti's Miraculous Medicine
7599.description: Remedy prescribed by Grand Seer Rahorakti for Dwarf Girl Kassandra
